<doc id="451567" wikidata="Q6779367" url="?curid=451567" title="Mary E. McAllister">
<text>Mary E. McAllister (April 20, 1937 – August 20, 2020) was a Democratic member of the North Carolina General Assembly representing the state&#x27;s forty-third House district, including constituents in Cumberland county. As of the 2003–04 session, McAllister was serving in her seventh term in the state House. She was an executive from Fayetteville, North Carolina.

