<doc id="451575" wikidata="Q5293919" url="?curid=451575" title="Donald A. Bonner">
<text>Donald Allen Bonner (June 22, 1935 – September 10, 2021) is a Democratic member of the North Carolina General Assembly representing the state&#x27;s forty-eighth House district, including constituents in Hoke, Robeson and Scotland counties. He is a retired educator from Rowland, North Carolina. Bonner died on September 10, 2021.

