<doc id="451583" wikidata="Q6730256" url="?curid=451583" title="Maggie Jeffus">
<text>Margaret A. Moore Jeffus (born October 22, 1934) is a former Democratic member of the North Carolina House of Representatives. A retired educator from Greensboro, Jeffus served constituents in Guilford County from 1991–2013.

