<text>Lindsey Hugh Holliman is a former Democratic member of the North Carolina General Assembly who represented the state&#x27;s eighty-first House district, including constituents in Davidson County. A self-employed businessman from Lexington, North Carolina, Holliman served six terms in the state House of Representatives until he was defeated by Republican Rayne Brown in the 2010 general election.

